##An 80-year-old mother, in tears, agreed to let me join the panel

Micro Signal Xinminzhoukan

Function description, depth and angle —— this is what we can do.

When people take off their masks, I will take off my protective clothing, reunite with my family, and raise a glass to my friends and family.

Dictation | Wang Weiwu

Finishing | Ying Chen

This Spring Festival is destined to be different from others.

February 13,2020, was the 16th day of my mission in Xianning. That night, I finally and third sister Wang Shuhong met on a side. She was political commissar of the police headquarters of the Xianning Public Security Bureau in Hubei Province, and has also been engaged in busy anti-epidemic work since the outbreak of the new crown pneumonia.

Wang Weiwu in the ward to understand the patient's condition

At the door of the hotel where our medical staff were staying, my third sister ran straight to me. I unconsciously took a few steps back, waved my hand at her and told her not to come near. Because here lives is the outside assistance medical personnel, every day goes in and out of the hospital, is too close not to be safe. In the dim light of the street, my third sister asked me carefully about my work situation. When I accidentally let slip that I only wore a mask to go around the major hospitals every day and didn't have any other protective equipment, third sister's tears flowed down uncontrollably.

01

My name is Wang Weiwu. I'm from Chongyang County, Hubei Province. I received my Ph. D. from the Chinese Academy of Traditional Chinese medicine and Karolinska Institutet in Sweden and worked as a postdoctoral researcher. After that, I settled in Sweden for many years, doing medical and scientific research work.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Treating foreigners in foreign countries

A few years ago, the family encountered some changes, in order to take care of my mother, I asked myself to return to China regularly every year. In China, I make house calls in the First Affiliated Hospital of Hunan University of Traditional Chinese medicine. Because Changsha is not far from Xianning, every time I return to China, I will certainly pick up my mother to live with Changsha, to do filial piety.

On House calls in the states,

This year is my mother's 80th birthday, very early we brothers and sisters will meet in the county home reunion. But the sudden outbreak of the disease, so that all the plans have come to nothing. Soon the city was closed, the roads were closed, and traffic was curbed. Third sister also in the first time into the work, she busy every day with various instructions, review all kinds of information data collection report, patrol social security situation, very tired.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Wang Weiwu (front row, first right) with his family

As a doctor, I couldn't sit at home and watch, so I asked third sister in the Wechat Group: "Now that the road is closed, is there any way I can travel? " Third sister immediately understood what I meant, but she didn't want me to risk it, then flatly rejected me: "there is no way, you peace of mind at home with the mother! "

Distraught, I unexpectedly received a call from the city's leadership. A tweet about me on wechat caught the attention of city party leaders, who contacted me after learning that I was from Xianning. So, January 27, I volunteered to join the leadership of the anti-epidemic medical experts. We hit it off after meeting the head of the Expert Group, Professor Du Guang of Tongji Medical College.

However, when I first heard the news, my family did not support my choice, especially my mother, who strongly disagreed. I spent the whole night working over and over on the Old Lady's ideas. In the meantime, my mother several tears let me very tangled. Since the death of her father at the age of 10, she was the one who brought up our five brothers and sisters, and I was her favorite youngest son, I understand her struggle.

At the time, I told her, "if there is an outbreak in Xianning, our little house will not be safe. It may seem dangerous, but I have the confidence that we will be able to protect ourselves and you need not worry about me. " Finally, mother gave her consent in tears.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Wang Weiwu (second from right) poses with Professor Du Guang, head of the Expert Group, and Wang Gang, director of the Department of Critical Care Medicine at the Tongji Medical College, and Vice President of the Second Hospital of Yunnan Province

On January 29th, I joined the team of medical experts in Xianning. Before leaving, the third sister reluctantly asked: "brother, you must go? You did not book a ticket to the United States, the next is not to go to Harvard Study? " See me firm attitude, the third sister will not say more.

02

After joining the panel, we didn't have a fixed amount of time to travel each day. 24 hours a day. Anything goes wrong, we're on our way. It's a very busy day and a very tight schedule.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
When the group went to Tongcheng County to guide its work, Comrade Xiong Yaping, secretary of the Tongcheng County County Party Committee, briefed the group on the epidemic prevention situation in Tongcheng County

Our main job is to go down to the districts and counties of Xianning, to make rounds in local hospitals, and to consult with them if we have any difficult problems. At the same time, we will go to the field to check the newly-opened medical fixed-point institution that will admit and treat the new coronary pneumonia, to see if its facilities and conditions are in place and meet the requirements. In addition, for those hospitals that have been designated as medical institutions, we should also check the fever clinics, isolation ward facilities are not standardized, the corresponding protection and disinfection measures are in place.

On January 31, I conducted a critical care consultation and was very impressed. He is a 65-year-old male patient, the condition has been very dangerous, CT films have "White Lung" , the Oxygenation is also relatively low, has appeared fever, chest tightness, dyspnea and other symptoms. After repeated expert group discussions, finally in addition to some conventional rescue methods, I used their own "double repair of Chinese and Western Medicine" background, prescribed some targeted Chinese medicine prescriptions. Happily, the patient has now been discharged from the hospital after our specialist's targeted treatment.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Expert consultation

Under normal circumstances, we will control the number of experts entering the ward consultation, because the first-line medical supplies are very scarce, in order to save protection resources, we will take online, offline remote and other ways to carry out consultation work.

Wang Weiwu checks the pulse of the patient in the intensive care unit

But traditional Chinese medicine pay attention to ask, ask and cut, pulse and tongue through the image is not transmitted. So, sometimes, I also go deep into intensive care ward rounds with other specialists at the hospital. Every time we enter the ward, we have to set up a level-three lockdown. And in order not to waste my isolation suit, I have to be in the ward no less than two hours at a time. The longest time, I went in for about four and a half hours, during which I could not eat, drink, pull, feel sweat like oil, wet and sticky body, the hard work of the first-line medical staff can be imagined.

In fact, teams of experts sometimes visit Chongyang County to inspect work, and my mother lives next to the People's Hospital in Chongyang County. My colleagues at the time were kind enough to suggest that I go back and visit my mother, but I thought about my daily activities in high risk areas such as the fever clinic and the isolation ward, and the fact that my mother was very old, although I missed her very much, but after much deliberation, he didn't go. That's happened three times.

Of course, when I have free time, I will call my mother, but not necessarily every day. Because sometimes from the hospital after a day's work back to the hotel at 11 o'clock at night, the mother has been asleep.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
In addition to the front line in the fight against the epidemic, Wang Weiwu also used his appeal at home and abroad to raise funds and materials. The picture shows materials donated to the People's Hospital of Chongyang County

As a doctor, I will continue to fight the virus. When people take off their masks, I will take off my protective clothing, reunite with my family, and raise a glass to my friends and family.
